Tests Mastermind's handling of guesses that contain whitespace before the
first letter and/or between letters.

For example:
   
   Enter the seed for random number generation: 2
   Enter the maximum letter for the game (A-Z): W
   Enter the number of positions for the game (1-8): 6
   Enter the number of guesses allowed for the game: 10

   Enter guess 1:                 A
        M                                  B
   AAA
   Nope, 0 exact guesses and 1 inexact guesses

   Enter guess 2: T T T T T T
   Nope, 1 exact guesses and 0 inexact guesses

   Enter guess 3: K                 A
   V
                         TP



  O

  Wow, you won in 3 guesses - well done!

